<exercise xmlns="https://spatext.clontz.org" version="0.0">
    <statement>
        <p>
            Find the radius of convergence and interval of convergence for the series: <me>\sum_{n=0}^\infty {{Sequence}}.</me>
            You don't need to check the endpoints, but you can if you are feeling spicy.
        </p>
        
    </statement>
    <answer>
            <ul>
                <li>The center of convergence is <m>{{center}}</m>.</li>
                <li>The radius of convergence is <m>{{radius}}</m>.</li>
                <li>The interval of convergence is <m>( {{left}}, {{right}} )</m>.</li>
            </ul>
    </answer>
</exercise>